#. type: multicols*
#: sections/solo_campaigns.tex:9
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"A Campaign is a series of Scenarios designed for solo play.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"战役是一系列为单人游戏设计的剧本。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/solo_campaigns.tex:13
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Starting a Scenario}\n"
"At the start of each Campaign Scenario, set your income by placing your Faction Cubes on spaces 10~\\svg{gold}, 0~\\svg{building_materials}, 0~\\svg{valuables} of the Resource Production Tracker on the Town Board. Special rules in each Scenario can change these values.\n"
"Campaigns have unique bonuses that \\textbf{replace} the regular starting bonus from the chosen \\pagelink{Difficulty}{Difficulty}.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{开始剧本}\n"
"在每个战役剧本开始时，将你的阵营方块放置在城镇板上资源生产轨道的10\\svg{gold}、0\\svg{building_materials}、0\\svg{valuables}格，以设定你的收入。每个剧本中的特殊规则可以改变这些数值。%\n"
"战役拥有独特奖励，会\\textbf{替代}所选\\pagelink{Difficulty}{难度}的常规初始奖励。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/solo_campaigns.tex:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Prepare AI Enemies: their \\pagelink{AI Heroes}{units} and their \\pagelink{AI Deck}{AI Decks}.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"准备AI敌人：他们的\\pagelink{AI Heroes}{单位}和\\pagelink{AI Deck}{AI牌堆}。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/solo_campaigns.tex:18
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Using different Heroes}\n"
"Although each campaign has its own recommended Hero for whom it is balanced and who is also the protagonist of the story, you are free to play with any other Hero of the same Faction.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{使用不同的英雄}\n"
"尽管每个战役都有其推荐的英雄，并围绕该英雄进行了平衡设计，且该英雄也是故事的主角，但你可以自由选择同一阵营的任何其他英雄进行游戏。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/solo_campaigns.tex:25
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If you choose to change your Hero between the Scenarios or when you repeat the Scenario with a different Hero,\n"
"replace all of the previous Hero’s Statistic cards and the Level I Specialty card with all of the Statistic cards and the Level I Specialty card of your new Hero.\n"
"If the previous Hero had \\pagelink{Empowered Statistic}{Empowered Statistics cards},\n"
"you can remove Statistic cards of the same type from the new Hero’s Deck, and replace them with Empowered Statistic cards of the corresponding type.\n"
"You can replace any card in the ``5 other non-Specialty cards'' group with new Hero’s starting Ability card (if you don't already have a copy of that Ability) and \\wikilink{spells/magic_arrow}{Magic Arrow(s).}\n"
"You cannot have more than 4 \\wikilink{spells/magic_arrow}{Magic Arrow} cards, even if the previous Hero had 5 of them.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"如果你选择在各剧本之间更换你的英雄，或使用不同英雄重复进行该剧本，%\n"
"将此前英雄的所有属性牌和等级I特长牌替换为新英雄的所有属性牌和等级I特长牌。%\n"
"如果此前英雄拥有\\pagelink{Empowered Statistic}{强化属性牌}，%\n"
"你可以从新英雄的牌堆中移除相同类型的属性牌，并用对应类型的强化属性牌替换它们。%\n"
"你可以将“5张其他非特长牌”组中的任意牌替换为新英雄的起始能力牌（如果你还没有该能力的一张副本）和\\wikilink{spells/magic_arrow}{魔法箭}。%\n"
"你不能拥有超过4张\\wikilink{spells/magic_arrow}{魔法箭}牌，即使此前英雄拥有5张也是如此。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/solo_campaigns.tex:28
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Combat}\n"
"See \\pagelink{AI Units}{Combat against AI} section.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{战斗}\n"
"参见\\pagelink{AI Units}{与AI战斗}章节。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/solo_campaigns.tex:38
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Finishing a Scenario}\n"
"After finishing a \\textbf{Solo Campaign} Scenario, reset your Hero's Experience Level to I, and prepare the starting Deck for the next Scenario of the Campaign.\n"
"It will consist of:\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item all the \\pagelink{Statistic}{Statistic} cards from your Deck,\n"
"  \\item Level I \\pagelink{Specialty}{Specialty} card,\n"
"  \\item 5 other non-Specialty cards of your choice from your Deck.\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"Skip \\pagelink{SetupStartingDeck}{steps \\ref*{SetupStartingDeck}--\\ref*{SetupStartingDeckEnd} of Setup} for the next Scenario of the Campaign.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{完成一个剧本}\n"
"完成一个\\textbf{单人战役}剧本后，将你的英雄的经验等级重置为I，并为该战役的下一个剧本准备起始牌堆。%\n"
"它将包含：\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item 你牌堆中所有\\pagelink{Statistic}{属性}牌，\n"
"  \\item 等级I\\pagelink{Specialty}{特长}牌，\n"
"  \\item 你牌堆中由你选择的其他5张非特长牌。\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"跳过该战役下一个剧本的\\pagelink{SetupStartingDeck}{准备的步骤\\ref*{SetupStartingDeck}--\\ref*{SetupStartingDeckEnd}}。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/solo_campaigns.tex:41
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Note down the list of cards in your starting Deck.\n"
"If you lose the Scenario, reset the Deck to the same list.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"记下你的起始牌堆中的牌列表。%\n"
"如果你输掉该剧本，将牌堆重置为相同的列表。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/solo_campaigns.tex:44
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\bigskip\n"
"\\note{6}{If your Hero is at some point given a Spell, Artifact, or Ability card that is unavailable, \\textbf{Search (3)} the respective card's Deck to get another card in its stead.}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\bigskip\n"
"\\note{6}{如果你的英雄在某个时刻获得了一张不可用的法术、神器或能力牌，\\textbf{搜寻（3）} 相应卡牌的牌堆，以获得另一张牌作为替代。}\n"
"\n"

